name: 魔女対魔女（WITCH V WITCH)
description:
There's so much I want to do, such as incorporate sounds and art. But you just gots yourself a DANMAKA!!!!! YAY!!!!!!!

Two witches confront each other to the death! And there's bullets flying all over the place!!!!

NO WAYYYYYY!!!!!

This is my first time making a Danmaku like this, and I  happen to be very proud. Danmaku's are one of my favorite genre of video games. And I also like Game Jams as well!!! This will count as my second one. 

Anyways, there's no sound, just intensity! I'll be most definitely be working on this more extensively in the near future! Til' then folks!!!
